The '''Great Spirit Tree''', also called the '''Great Tree''' or '''Spirit Tree''', was an ancient [[Tree/Legends|tree]] on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon of Endor]] that was sacred to the local [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]]. The [[Species/Legends|species]] believed that they were all descended from the Great Tree, and that all life eventually returned to it.

